HEADWORD: Provinciality
<hw>Pro*vin`ci*al"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
or state of being provincial; peculiarity of language characteristic of
a province.</def> <rj><au>T. Warton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
